{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"afb0d52f41","title":"我做了政治祭坛上的羔羊","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。原题为：“想！？………我做了政治祭坛上的羔羊………  ——一个“白毛女”说。”","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"368c075945","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"afb0d52f41"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"a5d45dc796","name":"王国乡"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e9533199ec","type":"title","text":"我做了政治祭坛上的羔羊","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"22d8fee5a6","type":"authors","text":"北京大学王国乡","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"ac0f9e3109","type":"subtitle","text":"（王国乡：北京大学中文系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"1ecf7228d2","type":"paragraph","text":"我有以下疑问，请您为我回答：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"267e7309ae","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“三反”时也整过官僚主义，而且几年以来我们一直在喊着反对官僚主义。这次整风后，“三害”是否还会复活？如何才能根除？","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"cf78c89615","type":"paragraph","text":"2．“三害”产生的根源，是否仅仅是党员个人的思想作风问题？如果是，为什么全国如此普遍？(看看最近的报纸吧！)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"b27a593ab3","type":"paragraph","text":"3．这次北大燃烧起来的民主的火焰，如此的激动人心，北京各报的记者都来过了，为什么报纸都仍然默默无声？难道所有的记者编辑部都还在坚持“三害”？","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"37d4ff2b09","type":"paragraph","text":"4．我听过一个亲手制造“白毛女”的干部说：“我们也是不得已啊……”似乎他也是一只羔羊。那么为什么？为什么？？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"e71364274b","type":"paragraph","text":"想想吧!为什么？","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"51b2e1c4cf","type":"paragraph","text":"当然，我不敢请那些只会体会领导意图的阿谀之辈来想，也不愿请那脑浆凝固，只剩下第一信号系统，条件反射的，宗教徒式的盲从和迷信的可怜虫来想。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"},{"id":"c18b8535a1","type":"paragraph","text":" 提问者  王国乡","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41"}],"page":{"id":"1710483891","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"afb0d52f41","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}